        {
            "title": "佰澤醫療下限定價超購近25倍  暗盤升近26%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地腫瘤醫療集團佰澤醫療(02609)下限4.22元定價，公開招股超額認購24.92倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"佰澤醫療官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/Bayzed-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"佰澤醫療官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/Bayzed-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">佰澤醫療官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">佰澤醫療國際配售部分認購不足，香港公開發售股份部分升至12.2%，總集資5.62億元，淨集資額4.678億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">基石投資者持股佔發售股份數目26.5%。控股股東上市後遵守禁售承諾的股份佔公司股權比例63.045%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一手600股中籤率20%，申請9000股旷5手穩獲一手。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">輝立暗盤價昨收報5.3元，較招股價升25.59%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">招銀國際為獨家保薦人。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15028617-%e4%bd%b0%e6%be%a4%e9%86%ab%e7%99%82%e4%b8%8b%e9%99%90%e5%ae%9a%e5%83%b9%e8%b6%85%e8%b3%bc%e8%bf%9125%e5%80%8d-%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%9126",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/Bayzed-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-21 13:15:28",
