            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "三花智能超購746倍上限定價   暗盤低收逾3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三花智能控股(02050)公布，公開招股超額認購746.92倍，上限22.53元定價。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國際配售超額22.75倍。集資淨額91.77億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：三花智能控制官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250604_FI_source-web_002050-4-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：三花智能控制官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250604_FI_source-web_002050-4-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：三花智能控制官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一手中籤率15%，申請2000股即20手穩獲一手。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">輝立暗盤收市較招股價低3.02%，報21.85元，一度低見19元，低15.67%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">香港公開招股觸發回撥機制，佔全球發售股份比例為26.5%，國際配售佔全球發售股份比例73.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">基石投資者持股佔已發行H股股份47.22%，佔已發行股木4.72%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15028533-%e4%b8%89%e8%8a%b1%e6%99%ba%e8%83%bd%e8%b6%85%e8%b3%bc746%e5%80%8d%e4%b8%8a%e9%99%90%e5%ae%9a%e5%83%b9-%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e9%80%be3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250604_FI_source-web_002050-4-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-21 12:56:15",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美債息報跌   兩年期債息跌逾3基點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國國債息率跌，債價全線升，聯儲局官員指最快7月可減息。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美國國債。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美國國債。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美國國債。</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約尾市，美國10年期基準國債收益率跌1.57個基點，報4.3751%，一度升4.8個基點，報4.444厘。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國10 年期國債本周累計下跌7.11個基點，一直處於下跌狀態，整體交投於4.4443%至4.3377%區間。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">對息口較敏感的2年期債息收益率跌3.337基點，報3.9077%，曾挫4.6基點，至3.895%。本周累跌5.87基點，整體交投於3.9749%至3.8824%區間。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">周三美聯儲宣布FOMC連續四次按兵不動、披露經濟預期概要時債息急劇下挫至本周最低位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">聯儲局理事沃勒(Christopher Waller)於CNBC訪問中指出，基於通脹情況許可，聯儲局最快可能於7月減息，但補充說有需要時可暫停減息。聯儲局主席鮑威爾下周出席國會聽證會，發表半年度貨幣政策報告。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐債方面，德國10年期國債收益率跌0.4個基點，報2.517%，本周累計下跌1.8個基點，交投於2.589%至2.486%區間，持續反覆下行。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國10年期國債收益率漲0.7個基點，報4.537%，本周累計下跌1.3個基點，整體交投於4.591%至4.494%區間。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15028434-%e7%be%8e%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e5%a0%b1%e8%b7%8c-%e5%85%a9%e5%b9%b4%e6%9c%9f%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be3%e5%9f%ba%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20190902_FI_US-TREASURY-BONDS_US-BOND_FB-1-2-1-1-1-1_source-web_-1-2-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-21 12:30:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
