            "title": "ADR低水112點   夜期低水134點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR較恆指昨日收市低收112點或0.48%，報23417點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：京東官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">主要股份ADR普遍低水，京東(09618) ADR較港收市價較港收市價低1.8%，報123.4元; 攜程(09961) ADR較香港收市價低1.8%，折合438.42元 ; 百度(09888) ADR較香港收市價低1%，折合82.05元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988) ADR較港收市價較港收市價低0.7%，折合110.89港元 ;  騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣502.4元，較香港收市價低0.6% ; 小米(01810) ADR較香港收市價低0.7%，折合53.68港元 ; 美團(03690) ADR較香港收市價低0.8%，折合127.56元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報91.73元，較香港收市價低0.6% ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣67.67元，較香港收市價低0.3% ;  港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣391.32元，較香港收市價低0.3%;  中國平安(02318) ADR收市折合港幣47.31元，較香港收市價低0.1% 。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報23396點，跌125點，較昨日恒指收市23530點，低水134點，成交12526張。國指夜市期指收報8481點，較昨日國指收市低水46點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15028399-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4112%e9%bb%9e-%e5%a4%9c%e6%9c%9f%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4134%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
